description: Dream Chicken NYC is serving up a savory selection of classic Indian fare with a casual and tasty twist, like their Veggie Fried Basmati Rice with Tandoori Chicken, or their Tandoori Chicken Wrap-tandoori grilled chicken breast wrapped in a warm, thin tortilla, and more!Come on out and try this food, you’re sure to find that this delicious Indian street cuisine is an absolute dream come true!
name: Dream Chicken NYC
